Interface IParser

All Known Implementing Classes:
CliGitAdd.GitAddParser, CliGitBranch.GitBranchParser, CliGitCheckout.GitCheckoutParser, CliGitCommit.GitCommitParser, CliGitLog.GitLogParser, CliGitMv.GitMvParser, CliGitReset.GitResetParser, CliGitStatus.GitStatusParser
public interface IParser

IParser is an interface for parsing a git command line output stream. See how implementations of IParser are used in ProcessUtilities.

See Also:
ProcessUtilities
